---
title: Chicken Jägerschnitzel & Mushroom Sauce with Potato Mash & Apple Salad
description: Jägerschnitzel, a hearty German delight, pairs tender breaded chicken with a rich mushroom sauce that’s perfect for a cosy feast. Potato mash soaks up extra sauce and acts as the ideal accompaniment for this dreamy combo!
